# OpenVINO model files (.xml + .bin) go here — not tracked by git (binary, large files)
# 
# Expected files:
#   models/ov/yolo11n.xml      + yolo11n.bin    (Zone Detector — person detection)
#   models/ov/rtmpose-t.xml    + rtmpose-t.bin  (Zone Detector — pose estimation)
#   models/ov/xg_detector.xml  + xg_detector.bin (XG Detector — proprietary)
#
# See README.md → "Model Files" section for download/conversion instructions.
